      <h3>Added</h3><ul>  <li>Offline build: the no-upload variant is now `macshot Offline` with its own bundle id, Sparkle feed, DMG, and Homebrew cask naming.</li>  </ul><h3>Fixed</h3><ul>  <li>Clipboard copies now keep retained backing files so Finder paste and clipboard history apps do not point at deleted temporary files.</li> <li>Clipboard copies include both image data and a file reference for better compatibility across paste targets.</li></ul>
